be lined up along the highway.

00:03:29.210 --> 00:03:32.470
While we are known as the
largest library in the world,

00:03:32.470 --> 00:03:36.840
what really matters of course
is content and quality.

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:38.620
We're fortunate to
have many divisions

00:03:38.620 --> 00:03:42.410
with subject matter experts
to provide research guidance

00:03:42.410 --> 00:03:45.810
and insight into these
massive collections

00:03:45.810 --> 00:03:48.560
