00:24:49.350 --> 00:24:53.250
The other great Euro-center
of culture

00:24:53.250 --> 00:24:56.900
and learning was Thessaloniki.

00:24:56.900 --> 00:25:00.980
And to Thessaloniki or Thessalonica
