00:25:09.370 --> 00:25:12.730
Here the Nazis succeeded.

00:25:12.730 --> 00:25:17.840
This was once one of the
biggest Jewish cities in Europe,

00:25:17.840 --> 00:25:23.000
like a center for a very
special Jewish community and one

00:25:23.000 --> 00:25:29.570
of the few European cities when
the Jewish population dominated.

00:25:29.570 --> 00:25:37.380
And this city had been founded
by Jews that left Spain in 1492

00:25:37.380 --> 00:25:42.990
after the Reconquista, when
