Thessaloniki in today's Greece,

00:26:18.330 --> 00:26:21.250
they took with them their books,

00:26:21.250 --> 00:26:26.810
and this city already during
the 16th century became known

00:26:26.810 --> 00:26:29.460
for its libraries, its culture.

00:26:29.460 --> 00:26:37.820
And when the Nazis came here almost
400 years later people still spoke

00:26:37.820 --> 00:26:43.500
Ladino, the ancient
Spanish-Jewish language.

00:26:43.500 --> 00:26:50.550
This was a society a
culture, a whole civilization

00:26:50.550 --> 00:26:56.450
