00:31:58.800 --> 00:32:02.060
and protect the Nazi ideology.

00:32:02.060 --> 00:32:06.390
And Rosenberg realized one thing,

00:32:06.390 --> 00:32:11.200
that the Nazi movement
wasn't held together

00:32:11.200 --> 00:32:16.010
by its ideology but
by something else.

00:32:16.010 --> 00:32:22.110
It was held together by the cult
surrounding the man in the middle,

00:32:22.110 --> 00:32:27.300
the cult, the Hitler
cult and the Fuhrer cult.

00:32:27.300 --> 00:32:32.760
Rosenberg believed that if the
man in the center disappeared,

00:32:32.760 --> 00:32:36.130 position:56%
