prisoners were added on top,

00:58:47.990 --> 00:58:52.580
and thereafter, another,
and another.

00:58:52.580 --> 00:58:55.990
When the Red Army reached
the scene a few days later,

00:58:55.990 --> 00:59:00.230
unburned bodies still
lay in the pyres.

00:59:00.230 --> 00:59:05.890
But one of the witnesses of Herman
Kruk's funeral managed to flee

00:59:05.890 --> 00:59:11.760 position:56%
and went back to dig up his diaries.

00:59:14.710 --> 00:59:17.670
